OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and bright with some
OL,6,Fmorning sunshine, becoming cloudy from
OL,7,Faround midday with outbreaks of rain
OL,8,Fand hill snow spreading from the south
OL,9,Fduring the afternoon. The easterly
OL,10,Fwind will strengthen later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy with further rain, and
OL,13,Fturning to snow to quite low levels
OL,14,Fover inland Moray, and Upper Deeside.
OL,15,FEasterly winds becoming northwest,
OL,16,Fsevere gale for time. Drier by morning.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSunday:FA dry and sunny morning.
OL,19,FCloudier for a time in afternoon with
OL,20,Fsome showers, wintry on high ground.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
