OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith some sunny spells on Monday then
OL,7,Fhigh cloud later. Sunny, breezy and
OL,8,Fwarm on Tuesday, cloudier later.
OL,9,FChance of patchy or rain or showers on
OL,10,FWednesday.
